 148:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****         (+) Enable the Power Controller (PWR) APB1 interface clock using the
 149:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****             RCC_APB1PeriphClockCmd() function.
 150:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****         (+) Enable access to RTC domain using the PWR_BackupAccessCmd() function.
