 502:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   * 
 503:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   * @note   This function can be used only for STM32F42xxx/STM3243xxx devices.
 504:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   * @note    This mode is enabled only with STOP low power mode.
 505:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   *          In this mode, the 1.2V domain is preserved in reduced leakage mode. This 
 506:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   *          mode is only available when the main regulator or the low power regulator 
