 508:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   *        
 509:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   * @note   If the Under-drive mode was enabled, it is automatically disabled after 
 510:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   *         exiting Stop mode. 
 511:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   *         When the voltage regulator operates in Under-drive mode, an additional  
 512:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   *         startup delay is induced when waking up from Stop mode.
 513:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   *                    
 514:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   * @param  NewState: new state of the Under Drive mode.
 515:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   *          This parameter can be: ENABLE or DISABLE.
 516:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   * @retval None
 517:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   */
 518:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c **** void PWR_UnderDriveCmd(FunctionalState NewState)
