 846:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   * @brief  Enters in Under-Drive STOP mode.
 847:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   *  
 848:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   * @note   This mode is only available for STM32F42xxx/STM3243xxx devices. 
