 851:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   *         
 852:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   * @note   In Stop mode, all I/O pins keep the same state as in Run mode.
 853:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   * @note   When exiting Stop mode by issuing an interrupt or a wakeup event, 
 854:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   *         the HSI RC oscillator is selected as system clock.
 855:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   * @note   When the voltage regulator operates in low power mode, an additional 
ARM GAS  C:\Users\asus\AppData\Local\Temp\ccK7S6kH.s 			page 32


 856:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   *         startup delay is incurred when waking up from Stop mode. 
 857:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   *         By keeping the internal regulator ON during Stop mode, the consumption 
 858:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   *         is higher although the startup time is reduced.
 859:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   *     
 860:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   * @param  PWR_Regulator: specifies the regulator state in STOP mode.
 861:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   *          This parameter can be one of the following values:
 862:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   *            @arg PWR_MainRegulator_UnderDrive_ON:  Main Regulator in under-drive mode 
 863:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   *                 and Flash memory in power-down when the device is in Stop under-drive mode
 864:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   *            @arg PWR_LowPowerRegulator_UnderDrive_ON:  Low Power Regulator in under-drive mode 
 865:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   *                and Flash memory in power-down when the device is in Stop under-drive mode
 866:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   * @param  PWR_STOPEntry: specifies if STOP mode in entered with WFI or WFE instruction.
 867:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   *          This parameter can be one of the following values:
 868:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   *            @arg PWR_STOPEntry_WFI: enter STOP mode with WFI instruction
 869:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   *            @arg PWR_STOPEntry_WFE: enter STOP mode with WFE instruction
 870:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   * @retval None
 871:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   */
