 911:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   * @note   In Standby mode, all I/O pins are high impedance except for:
 912:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   *          - Reset pad (still available) 
 913:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   *          - RTC_AF1 pin (PC13) if configured for tamper, time-stamp, RTC 
 914:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   *            Alarm out, or RTC clock calibration out.
