 916:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   *          - WKUP pin 1 (PA0) if enabled.
 917:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   * @note   The Wakeup flag (WUF) need to be cleared at application level before to call this funct
 918:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   * @param  None
 919:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_pwr.c ****   * @retval None
